何推进管理层的年轻化，成为投资者关心的热点之一。董明珠回应称，格力重视人才培养，不是以年龄、资历来衡量，关键在于人才的思想要保持年轻化，有创新能力、责任心及敢于拼搏。 「绝不用海归派，只在国内高校里培养自己的人才。」董明珠连任董事长称「绝不用海归」，张伟升任格力电器总裁"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-9b6204f050416417bce28a01bd154d18_1440w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "56 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1898336751686218417"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIxenflsqS/7t+EAMaCTExNDY0MTMwNSC+u6HABjAAOJYEQBxyEzE4OTgzMzY3NTE2ODYyMTg0MTd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1745464208.184947", "card_id": "Q_39836323", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 162}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "尼泊尔是一个怎样的国家?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "希望了解一下关于尼泊尔的政治，历史和经济情况，以及尼泊尔的城市化水平和特色，留作写作素材用。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-db3552298e186bbfca7b6a38f54f31ae_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "55 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/39836323"}}, "attached_info": "Cj0IxenflsqS/7t+EAMaBzgxNDE5MDUgtJaZtQUwADjeBkAdcggzOTgzNjMyM3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "is_start": false, "next": "", "previous": "", "totals": 0}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新", "display_num": 15, "display_first": true, "fb_bill_main_rise": 0, "head_zone": {"type": "billboard_lantern", "data": [{"id": "1898671729938773530", "link_url": "https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1898666300198347401?share_code=8e9jYFayZBbV&utm_psn=1898671088914900921", "title": "公安部网安局 | 防范木马病毒窃取数据", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTg5ODY3MTcyOTkzODc3MzUzMHITMTg5ODY3MTcyOTkzODc3MzUzMHgA", "tag": "关注", "tag_bg_color": "GRD01A"}, {"id": "1857515993426948096", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/appview/community_construction", "title": "辟谣专区", "so